title: Pandemic Influenza, Preparation and Response
description:
This is a 68 pages book from 2007 made by the Mid-peninsula Citizen's Preparedness Committee about hov to prepare and respond to a pandemic influenza. the book is light reading.
 
This file can also be found on Ingenfare.com a norwegian survivalism page.

This book is to the best of our knowledge CC, Fair Use, Public Domain, 
GPL or given permission from owner to copy and destribute.
